  "instructions": [
    "Drain the canned chickpeas and rinse them with cold water.",
    "Place the chickpeas in a large bowl.",
    "Add the chopped parsley, dill, mint, diced cucumber and nasturtium petals to the bowl.",
    "Whisk the olive oil, apple cider vinegar, mustard, honey and lemon juice together in a small jar.",
    "Season the vinaigrette with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Pour the dressing over the chickpeas and herbs.",
    "Toss the mixture gently until all ingredients are evenly coated.",
    "Let the salad sit for 5 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Serve the salad chilled or at room temperature.",
    "Garnish with a few extra fresh herbs if desired."
